{"tid":881463,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Apple 2018第二場發佈會（ 開定先 推到完場）","createTime":"2018-10-29T12:40:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-30T09:58:49.000Z","uid":219232,"like":9,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"d50f27ba719c072211c66b8f45de74964b29131e","tid":881463,"uid":219232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T12:40:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<strong><em>以下係關於發佈會的消息：</em></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/95EP3m5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F95EP3m5.png&h=044e461b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F31nDVD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF31nDVD.png&h=9d0b1504&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n關於 iPad Pro<br />\n<br />\n新款 iPad Pro 是 2015 年問世以來最重大的更新：<br />\n<br />\n採用全螢幕設計，超窄、對稱邊框，類似最新款 iPhone。<br />\n採用 USB-C 連接埠用於充電和傳輸數據，是 iOS 裝置首次採用該充電標準。<br />\n採用 Face ID 解鎖，移除主螢幕按鈕和指紋辨識功能，Face ID 支援橫直向辨識。<br />\n支援 Emoji / Animoji。<br />\n採用 LCD 螢幕，不是 iPhone X 系列的 OLED 螢幕。<br />\n外觀經過重新設計，更方正，類似 iPhone 5、5s 和 iPhone SE。<br />\nA12 仿生晶片的變種晶片。<br />\n蘋果自研圖形晶片，iPad 史上首次。<br />\n新款 Apple Pencil。<br />\n<br />\n關於 Mac<br />\n<br />\n自 2017 年 6 月以來首次大範圍更新 Mac 產品線，消息人士稱以下產品可能會在下週發表：<br />\n<br />\n全新入門級筆電取代 MacBook Air，採用更高解析度的 13 吋螢幕，超窄邊框設計。<br />\n自 2014 年首次更新 Mac mini，配置全新處理器及為專業用戶準備的功能。<br />\n蘋果還打算更新 iMac、iMac Pro 及 12 吋 MacBook，其中有些可能會在下週發表。<br />\n<br />\n紐約布魯克林音樂學院已準備就緒，我們拭目以待吧。<br />\n<br />\n資料來自<a href=\"https://technews.tw/2018/10/29/new-ipad-pro-macbook/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftechnews.tw%2F2018%2F10%2F29%2Fnew-ipad-pro-macbook%2F&d=TH25f6O4l%2BkW713sTJIbZhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=8b580ff5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://technews.tw/2018/10/29/new-ipad-pro-macbook/</a>"},{"pid":"aa9a84550472e2896f184cbd8779aed8e363a38e","tid":881463,"uid":219232,"like":36,"dislike":59,"score":-23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T12:44:23.000Z","msg":"各位巴絲打比較期待邊樣？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> New iPad Pro<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> New MacBook Air"},{"pid":"c196cd6f8dbb3ec54d43c6594d29fc7dcba00c58","tid":881463,"uid":30067,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T12:56:54.000Z","msg":"我要買新macbook 呀！！！！"},{"pid":"ec24eb85edf3befeecf47601e0edb1d134e34768","tid":881463,"uid":219232,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T13:04:45.000Z","msg":"新iPad Pro 會咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mWok99w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmWok99w.jpg&h=83b2df74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZE1feCN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZE1feCN.jpg&h=db0b815f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b42b59f702a5ed38eafcb4eb1eae95721ee2da22","tid":881463,"uid":27432,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"c